00:43:07,830 --> 00:43:10,230
No. Gu Ddol Ah.

485
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:16,750
Gu Ddol, It's your older brother! Come back to your senses!

486
00:43:16,750 --> 00:43:19,740
Gu Ddol! Gu Ddol!

487
00:43:23,420 --> 00:43:25,540
You're okay.

488
00:43:29,550 --> 00:43:32,160
This really does not make sense.

489
00:43:38,350 --> 00:43:40,560
How can we put a stake in the river in a situation like this?

490
00:43:40,560 --> 00:43:42,340
How can we put up a temporarily bridge?

491
00:43:42,340 --> 00:43:47,860
I said they already sent them the message twice that the march is no longer possible.

492
00:43:47,860 --> 00:43:53,740
But they keep pushing us to do it, what can we do about it?

493
00:43:55,300 --> 00:44:00,500
While trying to put a stake on the river, more hundred men in Troop 1 died,

494
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:03,130
when we did not even see the enemy...

495
00:44:04,310 --> 00:44:09,430
We couldn't even retrieve the corpses. They all went down river.

496
00:44:14,760 --> 00:44:17,430
No, what are you saying?

497
00:44:17,430 --> 00:44:20,000
They still haven't crossed the Yalu river yet?

498
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:24,220
Because of daily torrential rain that causes the water in the Yalu River to flood, the river-crossing attempts continue to fail.

499
00:44:24,220 --> 00:44:27,000
Didn't we already expect all of that?

500
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:31,120
Every time we get a report, there's always a serious problem appearing. They must cross the river.

501
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:34,200
But if the soldiers will suffer from unreasonably crossing the river...

502
00:44:34,200 --> 00:44:40,380
If it gets too late and they can't secure a supply line, they will suffer more than that.

503
00:44:41,960 --> 00:44:44,520
Damn it!

504
00:44:44,520 --> 00:44:49,640
Could Lee Seong Gye be having different thoughts?

505
00:44:49,640 --> 00:44:52,320
This won't do. I need to see the king.

506
00:44:52,320 --> 00:44:56,760
I need to send the royal command to the inspector to encourage them to advance.

507
00:44:58,320 --> 00:45:02,620
We failed again.

508
00:45:03,760 --> 00:45:05,770
The others were the same.

509
00:45:05,770 --> 00:45:11,060
The current is too strong so we couldn't drive in the posts.

510
00:45:11,060 --> 00:45:14,200
And yet, the number of soldiers who have fallen into the water...

511
00:45:15,040 --> 00:45:19,800
The number of soldiers... is unknown.

512
00:45:19,800 --> 00:45:23,350
Even now, the numbers keep on changing.

513
00:45:26,910 --> 00:45:32,560
Isn't military provision a problem? The deadline for us to cross the river has already passed.

514
00:45:32,560 --> 00:45:38,840
Wasn't the original plan to seize Liaodong and gather provisions on site?

515
00:45:38,840 --> 00:45:45,160
At this rate, even if we cross the river, it will be hard to get supplies.

516
00:45:45,160 --> 00:45:49,210
Because we were dispatched at a time when the harvest is not yet ripe,

517
00:45:49,210 --> 00:45:51,750
isn't that obvious?

518
00:45:53,760 --> 00:45:57,150
Genereal, an epedemic is going around.

519
00:45:57,150 --> 00:46:00,170
For now, we have found those who are affected and isolated them

520
00:46:00,170 --> 00:46:03,030
but it is spreading at an alarming rate.

521
00:46:03,030 --> 00:46:09,490
Can you not request a withdrawal?

522
00:46:16,240 --> 00:46:18,210
What is it this time?

523
00:46:23,310 --> 00:46:25,910
Why are you doing this?

524
00:46:27,000 --> 00:46:30,510
General. You need to withdraw the troops.

525
00:46:30,510 --> 00:46:32,590
We tried to withdraw twice

526
00:46:32,590 --> 00:46:34,090
but the king said we could not.

527
00:46:34,090 --> 00:46:41,040
Without acknowledging the royal command, please withdraw the troops, General.

528
00:46:44,940 --> 00:46:50,720
At this rate, even if we succeed to cross the Yalu River and arrive into Liaodong, among the 50,000 soldiers,

529
00:46:50,720 --> 00:46:54,180
there will be only half of them left to fight.

530
00:46:54,180 --> 00:46:56,810
Even before we start the battle, we will lose.

531
00:46:56,810 --> 00:46:58,780
We can't!

532
00:47:00,830 --> 00:47:03,190
All of the general's family members

533
00:47:03,190 --> 00:47:08,970
in Gaegyeong and Seogyeong are held hostage.

534
00:47:13,500 --> 00:47:16,360
If we disobey the royal command,

535
00:47:16,360 --> 00:47:22,200
all of the general's family members will die. That's what I'm saying.

536
00:47:30,240 --> 00:47:33,980
Han Nom, Han Nom. Han Nom!

537
00:47:36,250 --> 00:47:37,950
Han Nom!

538
00:47:41,750 --> 00:47:43,920
Han Nom...

539
00:47:43,920 --> 00:47:47,430
Han Nom...

540
00:47:50,220 --> 00:47:51,920
Han Nom!

541
00:47:53,860 --> 00:47:55,110
Are you crazy? Move!

542
00:47:55,110 --> 00:47:56,690
He's my brother. My brother...

543
00:47:56,690 --> 00:47:59,300
Do you also want to catch the plague?

544
00:47:59,300 --> 00:48:01,370
I don't care. Han Nom!

545
00:48:01,370 --> 00:48:05,290
We all appear to be thinking that each of us is dying.

546
00:48:05,290 --> 00:48:10,410
Move back. There are a lot of people here who feel the same way you do.

547
00:48:13,560 --> 00:48:19,310
Hyung... Don't worry. They said they will give me medicine.

548
00:48:19,310 --> 00:48:26,000
If I take the medicine, I'll get better. Don't worry.

549
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:28,090
But Han Nom...

550
00:48:31,060 --> 00:48:32,980
What is this...

551
00:48:34,620 --> 00:48:36,680
Something like this...

552
00:48:38,040 --> 00:48:41,260
Why is something like this called war?

553
00:48:41,260 --> 00:48:43,390
It is war.

554
00:48:44,890 --> 00:48:49,260
This here is war.

555
00:48:56,170 --> 00:49:00,050
Aren't you Hanbusa Kim? Are you here with the royal command?

556
00:49:00,050 --> 00:49:03,470
Do you have an answer from His Highness?

557
00:49:04,990 --> 00:49:11,010
That's right. General Lee Seong Gye, receive the royal command.

558
00:49:20,690 --> 00:49:25,170
His Higness ordered that you must immediately cross the Yalu River

559
00:49:25,170 --> 00:49:28,150
and advance to Liaodong.

560
00:49:28,150 --> 00:49:33,730
To send you the King's encouragement for your advancement to cross the river, I came all the way here.

561
00:49:35,160 --> 00:49:40,250
How is it that you're still doing nothing here?

562
00:49:40,250 --> 00:49:44,330
You were supposed to cross the river before the 7th,

563
00:49:44,330 --> 00:49:47,200
so if you are not having different thoughts

564
00:49:47,200 --> 00:49:49,980
why are you being like this?

565
00:49:51,660 --> 00:49:55,610
Go out and look at the condition of the Yalu River before you say that.

566
00:49:55,610 --> 00:49:59,600
Because of the plan to cross the river, many soldiers have already died.

567
00:49:59,600 --> 00:50:03,940
General Choi Yeong told me to relay this to you.

568
00:50:05,180 --> 00:50:11,280
"There's no battlefield with no hardships."

569
00:50:15,680 --> 00:50:17,300
General.

570
00:50:19,160 --> 00:50:21,130
General.

571
00:50:21,130 --> 00:50:22,150
What happened?

572
00:50:22,150 --> 00:50:26,460
The Ga Byeol Cho has caught deserters again.

573
00:50:27,660 --> 00:50:29,800
The number of deserters is increasing.

574
00:50:29,800 --> 00:50:34,460
I think you should make a decision now.

575
00:51:08,410 --> 00:51:11,200
You bastards!

576
00:51:11,200 --> 00:51:13,330
Leaving your comrades behind,

577
00:51:13,330 --> 00:51:17,090
did you escape to just save yourselves?

578
00:51:18,130 --> 00:51:20,670
You will be punished...

579
00:51:24,510 --> 00:51:27,440
You will be punished

580
00:51:29,440 --> 00:51:34,780
and it will be an example of stern the royal command is.

581
00:51:34,780 --> 00:51:37,040
Execute them!

582
00:51:45,760 --> 00:51:51,320
I got dragged while boiling porridge without knowing the reason why.

583
00:51:51,320 --> 00:51:53,610
Please send me back to my hometown.

584
00:51:53,610 --> 00:51:55,810
Forget it! Just kill me!

585
00:51:55,810 --> 00:52:01,080
Anyway, whether it's from the plague or from running away,

586
00:52:01,080 --> 00:52:05,250
it is obvious the we will die without even fighting the enemy.

587
00:52:05,250 --> 00:52:09,330
To get rid of the Yeojin tribe or the Ming, I volunteered and came here

588
00:52:09,330 --> 00:52:12,720
but what is this?

589
00:52:30,110 --> 00:52:32,450
What are you doing?

590
00:52:32,450 --> 00:52:35,320
Hurry and execute them according to the military law.

591
00:52:37,540 --> 00:52:40,360
Hurry and cut their heads off!

592
00:52:41,360 --> 00:52:44,230
Look at this bastard.

593
00:52:50,010 --> 00:52:52,970
You bastard! Just what are you doing?

594
00:52:52,970 --> 00:52:55,660
Put down your sword this instant!

595
00:52:56,580 --> 00:52:58,720
I can't.

596
00:53:02,200 --> 00:53:04,840
Why are we traitors?

597
00:53:04,840 --> 00:53:08,150
Those honorable bastards are not traitors so why

598
00:53:08,150 --> 00:53:11,080
am only I, who is powerless, the traitor?

599
00:53:11,080 --> 00:53:13,910
Chung Gil, you!

600
00:53:13,910 --> 00:53:17,670
Are you going to betray me after disobeying the army?

601
00:53:17,670 --> 00:53:20,020
The betrayal

602
00:53:25,640 --> 00:53:27,560
is by you, General

603
00:53:27,560 --> 00:53:28,690
What?

604
00:53:28,690 --> 00:53:31,030
When you saved me who pretended

605
00:53:31,030 --> 00:53:34,190
to be a Japanese pirate to save my son,

606
00:53:34,190 --> 00:53:36,780
what did you say, General?

607
00:53:36,780 --> 00:53:40,930
Not just my own children but other people's children and families as well.

608
00:53:40,930 --> 00:53:45,330
You told me to stay in the Ga Byeol Cho to save them all.

609
00:53:45,330 --> 00:53:47,040
But what is this?

610
00:53:47,040 --> 00:53:52,000
The 50,000 people here are someone else's sons.

611
00:53:52,000 --> 00:53:58,820
To these people, there are a a total of 100,000 mothers and fathers.

612
00:53:58,820 --> 00:54:05,870
If we continue this war, you will take 50,000 children to those 100,000 parents.

613
00:54:05,870 --> 00:54:08,330
What are you going to do with the blood and tears

614
00:54:08,330 --> 00:54:11,870
that you're being like this?

615
00:54:16,940 --> 00:54:19,430
Kill me.

616
00:54:19,430 --> 00:54:21,980
I cannot

617
00:54:21,980 --> 00:54:24,730
kill these people.

618
00:54:34,850 --> 00:54:38,920
What are you doing? Immediately arrest this person!

619
00:54:49,550 --> 00:54:51,410
General.

620
00:54:52,470 --> 00:54:56,230
I honestly didn't know that night.

621
00:54:57,530 --> 00:54:59,440
But now I do.

622
00:54:59,440 --> 00:55:01,910
On that night!

623
00:55:04,090 --> 00:55:07,130
The horse that you set out in Gaegyeong

624
00:55:07,870 --> 00:55:10,370
should not have been the white horse

625
00:55:10,370 --> 00:55:12,800
but the black horse.

626
00:55:25,420 --> 00:55:27,580
General.

627
00:55:28,840 --> 00:55:31,140
My siblings...

628
00:55:31,980 --> 00:55:34,920
Please save my siblings.

629
00:55:39,940 --> 00:55:44,650
The younger and older brothers who came here to Wihwa Island,

630
00:55:44,650 --> 00:55:49,520
please save them, General!

631
00:55:57,900 --> 00:56:01,340
Just what are you doing?

632
00:56:01,340 --> 00:56:05,900
Arrest these people and immediately kill them.

633
00:56:05,900 --> 00:56:09,560
How can the army, that is supposed to lead, be doing this?

634
00:56:11,170 --> 00:56:15,700
General, the 'Guk' character in country

635
00:56:15,700 --> 00:56:20,460
is made up of the characters, spear, land, and people.
(protecting the land and people with a spear)

636
00:56:20,460 --> 00:56:22,710
This is a country.

637
00:56:22,710 --> 00:56:27,650
If you put the 'Guk' character of country with this one,

638
00:56:27,650 --> 00:56:32,420
it transforms into 'by protecting the land and the people with a spear, you gain family.'

639
00:56:32,420 --> 00:56:35,850
This is a nation.

640
00:56:39,600 --> 00:56:41,500
General!

641
00:56:41,500 --> 00:56:46,710
Immediately enact military discipline and execute them. Hurry!

642
00:56:49,810 --> 00:56:51,660
Wife,

643
00:56:53,410 --> 00:56:54,950
Hyung-nim...

644
00:56:54,950 --> 00:56:59,540
Bang Woo, Bang Gwa, Bang Ui,

645
00:56:59,540 --> 00:57:01,110
Why are you being like this?

646
00:57:01,110 --> 00:57:05,690
Bang Gan, Bang Won, Bang Beon, Bang Seok...

647
00:57:07,780 --> 00:57:10,620
My children...

648
00:57:10,620 --> 00:57:12,970
Hyung-nim...

649
00:57:14,870 --> 00:57:20,020
If we disobey the royal command, all of the General's family members will die.

650
00:57:20,020 --> 00:57:21,920
That's what I'm saying.

651
00:57:21,920 --> 00:57:26,850
Isn't a king supposed to take care of the people first?

652
00:57:26,850 --> 00:57:32,770
But my choice will always be my family.

653
00:57:33,880 --> 00:57:36,100
I'm sorry...

654
00:57:38,420 --> 00:57:40,930
I

655
00:57:40,930 --> 00:57:43,310
will do it like this.

656
00:57:44,450 --> 00:57:47,920
If you can't do it, then I will!

657
00:57:54,640 --> 00:57:56,500
Stop!

658
00:58:02,500 --> 00:58:07,720
Immediately arrest Kim Hwan,

659
00:58:07,720 --> 00:58:09,610
Yes!

660
00:58:10,850 --> 00:58:13,050
What?

661
00:58:18,210 --> 00:58:20,650
I, Lee Seong Gye!

662
00:58:20,650 --> 00:58:24,540
If you spread your fence around the whole country,

663
00:58:24,540 --> 00:58:26,590
that is a nation

664
00:58:26,590 --> 00:58:30,770
and that's also being a king.

665
00:58:31,610 --> 00:58:33,960
I, Lee Seong Gye,

666
00:58:34,730 --> 00:58:38,460
will not cross the Yalu River!

667
00:58:51,000 --> 00:58:53,510
Joseon's first king

668
00:58:53,510 --> 00:58:56,050
Tae Jo Lee Seong Gye

669
00:59:03,750 --> 00:59:07,050
Your whole family is being held hostage right now but you're withdrawing the troops?

670
00:59:07,050 --> 00:59:10,720
Do I look like someone who can live after killing 50,000 soldiers?

671
00:59:10,720 --> 00:59:14,240
You're not going to cross the Yalu River? Are you going to commit treason?

672
00:59:14,240 --> 00:59:17,740
Whatever method you use, you must save Sister-in-law and the children.

673
00:59:17,740 --> 00:59:20,360
What do you think is the most important choice?

674
00:59:20,360 --> 00:59:22,220
It's a matter of choosing your enemy.

675
00:59:22,220 --> 00:59:24,200
My 50,000 sons!

676
00:59:24,200 --> 00:59:27,460
Today, to our families, who are waiting for us,

677
00:59:27,460 --> 00:59:30,030
we are going back!
